<div style="font-size:12px;">
<div style="font-size:14px;"><span class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle fa-fw fa-lg"></span><strong>Due to the cpp.edu and <a href="//www.cpp.edu/~office365/">Office 365 Email</a> migration, you will need to re-configure the email preview if you wish to use it.</strong></div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The email inbox preview below will let you see if you have new email and peek at messages in your Cal Poly Pomona mail account.</p>
<p>To setup the email preview, click the link "Configure this portlet now", enter your BroncoName and BroncoPassword, and then click "Save Settings" button.</p>
<p>After setup is completed, you can read the message, see if the message has any attachments, and delete unwanted messages. You <em>cannot</em> send or reply to messages using this preview.</p>
<p>For a fully-featured email client, click on the "Inbox" link and you will be directed to login to the web-based version of your Cal Poly Pomona email system.</p>
</div>
